org.friendlysnmp

Class FConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.friendlysnmp.FConverter

  • public class FConverter
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains collection of static methods to convert java.lang objects to and from org.snmp4j.smi.Variable

    The code is based on converter used in SNMP-FD - Failure Detection service based on SNMP by Matthias Wiesmann http://ddg.jaist.ac.jp/en/projects/snmp-fd/

    Version:
    $Revision: 1.21 $

      • toInt

        public static final int toInt(java.util.BitSet bs)
        SNMP enumerates bits from left-to-right with 0-based index. The bit 0 is a sign bit, and so on. Only first 32 bits from BitSet parameter are used to set bits for resulting int value.
        Parameters:
        bs - BitSet with first 32 bits considered
        Returns:
        int value with bits set
